            "id": 6011003,
            "title": "〈台幣〉觀望氣氛濃厚微貶收29.931元 周線終止連9揚",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DXY\">美元指數</a>持續走軟，市場聚焦稍晚公布的美國非農就業報告，使得匯市交投清淡，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>兌美元今 (6) 日收在 29.931 元、微貶 0.9 分，台北及元太外匯市場總成交值收斂至 15.42 億美元。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011003%2Fl%2F559207b51aecf48dd0f1c10dccdf1a93.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台幣〉觀望氣氛濃厚微貶收29.931元 周線終止連9揚。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>兌美元匯率本周陷入盤整，在 29.9、30 元附近整理，累計小貶 0.2 分或 0.01%，周線終止連 9 揚紀錄。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台北匯市今天交投冷清，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>兌美元以 29.9 元開盤，最高來到 29.897 元、最低 29.939 元，匯價波動幅度不大。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察主要貨幣今天對美元表現，根據央行統計，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DXY\">美元指數</a>小漲 0.05%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/eurusd\">歐元</a>升值 0.13%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/jpyusd\">日元</a>回貶 0.39%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>、新加坡幣及<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>約貶 0.02-0.03%。韓國股匯休市一天。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>聯準會 (Fed) 決策官員預計將於 6 月 17 至 18 日舉行 FOMC 會議，決定最新利率政策，市場屏息以待，由於美國經濟基本面仍然穩健，期貨市場普遍押注此次將按兵不動，不過，有官員透露，若近期貿易政策的不確定性得以化解，Fed 還是有可能啟動降息。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
